WEBVTT

00:57.640 --> 00:58.600
Is that…

01:06.775 --> 01:07.650
No way.

01:14.074 --> 01:16.659
GREETINGS, DEAR SUBSCRIBER

01:44.604 --> 01:45.438
You made it?

01:46.564 --> 01:47.398
Who are you?

01:49.484 --> 01:51.236
Let's see.

01:52.946 --> 01:56.658
Seo Mi-rae, 29, heterosexual.

01:57.867 --> 01:58.701
Right?

02:00.286 --> 02:01.287
Yes.

02:01.788 --> 02:04.415
Would you happen to be an actual person?

02:05.083 --> 02:08.878
I'm your designated dating manager.
Call me Unni if you want.

02:11.840 --> 02:16.094
But where are we?
I mean, what's with all those posters?

02:17.720 --> 02:18.888
Just a sec.

02:33.278 --> 02:34.404
Your hand.

02:37.991 --> 02:40.535
Those who come here
are each given this ring.

02:41.202 --> 02:43.955
It'll appear on you automatically
every time you log in.

02:44.038 --> 02:45.748
Take it off, and you'll log out.

02:46.541 --> 02:50.420
So you're saying this place
is a virtual reality, aren't you?

02:51.087 --> 02:52.380
Yeah.

02:53.256 --> 02:55.466
What about me? Is my body safe at home?

02:56.384 --> 02:57.218
Probably?

03:08.897 --> 03:10.857
All right. Let's get going now.

03:11.733 --> 03:12.567
Where to?

03:24.204 --> 03:26.122
THE MAN YOU THINK YOU KNOW

03:26.206 --> 03:27.207
Enter.

03:28.291 --> 03:29.334
What?

03:58.238 --> 03:59.072
What the…

04:02.659 --> 04:03.618
Wait a second.

04:07.622 --> 04:10.416
This is Choi Si-woo.

04:14.254 --> 04:18.049
Congratulations, Ms. Seo Mi-rae,
on meeting your first date!

04:31.229 --> 04:33.022
I can't believe how handsome he is.

04:41.114 --> 04:43.032
Are you okay?

04:46.452 --> 04:47.662
Oh my God!

04:49.038 --> 04:50.039
Who…

04:53.584 --> 04:56.004
Take it off, and you'll log out.

05:16.316 --> 05:18.484
EPISODE 2
CLICHE OR CLASSIC

05:19.152 --> 05:20.320
BOYFRIEND ON DEMAND

05:21.112 --> 05:24.782
DU showcases its technology.
Experience BoD with all five senses.

05:24.866 --> 05:27.910
Boyfriend on Demand,
coming soon to redefine romance.

05:27.994 --> 05:29.287
Concerns over addiction.

05:32.415 --> 05:36.252
When the door to everyday life closes,
a new door opens,

05:36.794 --> 05:39.797
and the date
you've been dreaming of begins.

05:40.423 --> 05:41.758
Ready for another dreamy day?

05:43.509 --> 05:46.763
This is a place where any romance
you desire becomes reality.

05:47.388 --> 05:50.141
There are 900 themes just for you.

05:50.641 --> 05:53.936
So who will you be dating today?

06:04.614 --> 06:06.616
Min Jun-young, you bastard.

06:08.534 --> 06:10.078
I respect the hell out of you.

06:19.587 --> 06:21.798
When you experience something surreal,

06:22.590 --> 06:24.675
it takes time to process it.

06:42.819 --> 06:43.861
Ms. Seo.

06:48.950 --> 06:50.993
Dong-min told me to bring this to you.

06:53.162 --> 06:55.915
Oh, right. You can leave it there.

06:55.998 --> 06:57.917
-I'll put it here.
-Yeah.

07:09.512 --> 07:12.807
What? You want to move
Hwany's webtoon to Fridays?

07:12.890 --> 07:14.183
Take a look at this.

07:14.684 --> 07:18.688
It's the list of our Friday webtoons.
Don't you think it's outdated?

07:18.771 --> 07:21.441
And just look at the ratings
for The Man to Know.

07:21.524 --> 07:22.400
It's hopeless.

07:22.483 --> 07:24.986
But Hwany's really catching on.

07:25.069 --> 07:27.780
I doubt he'd want to compete with Ms. Yun.

07:27.864 --> 07:30.366
That's why you should just
float the idea to him.

07:31.826 --> 07:33.661
What's wrong? You don't want to?

07:34.871 --> 07:36.164
No, it's not that.

07:36.956 --> 07:38.541
I just don't see why

07:38.624 --> 07:41.586
you'd have two popular authors
competing on the same day.

07:41.669 --> 07:44.922
I have no intention of betting
this company's fate on one person.

07:45.673 --> 07:48.676
Hwany does everything
you tell him to do anyway.

07:48.759 --> 07:51.762
Just mention it to him, okay?

07:52.263 --> 07:53.181
Well?

07:55.308 --> 07:57.018
Sure. I'll do that.

07:57.101 --> 07:58.227
Okay.

07:58.311 --> 08:00.730
-All right. Get back to work.
-Yes, sir.

08:04.567 --> 08:05.401
Sir?

08:06.777 --> 08:08.946
Is Seo Mi-rae also aware of this?

08:09.030 --> 08:10.656
She doesn't need to know.

08:10.740 --> 08:12.867
If Yun Song finds out, we'll be done for!

08:13.493 --> 08:15.703
We'll act first, think later.

08:17.538 --> 08:18.456
I see.

08:23.669 --> 08:26.005
This is uncomfortable.

08:32.970 --> 08:34.597
It's just a drawing.

08:35.097 --> 08:36.224
Get a grip.

08:58.829 --> 09:00.957
NAEMO'S BEST FRIDAY WEBTOON
THE MAN TO KNOW

09:02.625 --> 09:04.210
Was this here before?

09:08.506 --> 09:09.507
CAN I… STAY THE NIGHT?

09:10.967 --> 09:12.051
What?

09:20.560 --> 09:22.645
WANT A SHARPER NOSE THAN A WEBTOON LEAD?
PEOPLE PLASTIC SURGERY

09:22.728 --> 09:23.854
Isn't Choi Si-woo so cool?

09:23.938 --> 09:25.273
I know, right?

09:27.275 --> 09:28.192
THE MAN TO KNOW

09:30.987 --> 09:32.029
THE MAN TO KNOW

09:33.990 --> 09:35.241
THE MAN TO KNOW, VOL. 1

09:39.829 --> 09:41.163
Everywhere I look,

09:41.998 --> 09:43.207
there's Choi Si-woo.

09:51.465 --> 09:54.844
THE MAN TO KNOW
NAEMO'S NO. 1 WEBTOON IN STORES

10:35.051 --> 10:37.345
What? Where am I?

10:52.443 --> 10:55.321
Eun Na-ra, the female lead
of The Man to Know, is a hotelier.

10:57.239 --> 11:01.035
Am I supposed to experience the life
of a female lead in a webtoon?

11:07.750 --> 11:09.418
APPROVAL REQUEST

11:09.502 --> 11:10.836
"General manager"?

11:26.686 --> 11:28.979
GENERAL MANAGER CHOI SI-WOO

11:31.232 --> 11:32.358
It really is him.

11:34.193 --> 11:36.028
He really was Choi Si-woo.

11:41.325 --> 11:45.037
It appears an employee had the nerve
to sit on my desk.

11:46.831 --> 11:47.790
Was I seeing things?

11:49.250 --> 11:51.460
-No, it's just--
-Get out. Now.

12:02.263 --> 12:03.139
What's his problem?

12:04.557 --> 12:05.558
Wait.

12:14.859 --> 12:16.527
I thought you wanted me to leave.

12:18.487 --> 12:20.072
Have we met before?

12:21.866 --> 12:23.033
There it is.

12:41.719 --> 12:44.138
Oh my God. This is insane!

12:52.438 --> 12:56.025
You, you must be from…

12:57.318 --> 12:58.235
That's right.

12:59.779 --> 13:01.197
But how are you here?

13:02.948 --> 13:04.992
Because I work here?

13:08.496 --> 13:09.997
I finally found you.

13:11.123 --> 13:14.460
Ever since the day you saved me…

13:16.462 --> 13:19.298
not a day has gone by
without me thinking of you.

13:19.882 --> 13:21.467
Wait, what's he doing?

13:21.550 --> 13:22.927
I never forgot about you

13:24.678 --> 13:26.096
for a single moment.

13:27.598 --> 13:29.225
I had forgotten

13:29.308 --> 13:32.603
how cheesy The Man to Know was.

13:33.604 --> 13:36.023
That's sweet,
but that came out of nowhere--

13:36.106 --> 13:36.941
Wait.

13:38.317 --> 13:39.902
Let me look for just a moment.

13:40.986 --> 13:41.821
Look at what?

13:43.656 --> 13:44.532
It's here.

13:46.992 --> 13:47.827
What is?

13:48.994 --> 13:50.704
The face I've been longing for

13:51.789 --> 13:55.209
and desperately searching for
in my dreams…

13:58.546 --> 13:59.672
every night.

14:07.388 --> 14:08.430
Oh shit!

14:11.684 --> 14:14.562
Is he deranged?
That's more cringe than anyone can handle.

14:25.030 --> 14:25.990
It's here.

14:26.490 --> 14:28.075
The face I've been longing for

14:28.158 --> 14:31.996
and desperately searching for
in my dreams every night.

14:32.580 --> 14:33.414
I can't take this.

14:39.795 --> 14:41.213
Can't stand the sight of him?

14:42.214 --> 14:44.842
Such disrespect
for a hero going off to war.

14:45.342 --> 14:46.176
Poor Si-woo.

14:47.094 --> 14:48.929
War? What are you on about?

14:49.889 --> 14:52.349
-You haven't seen Hwany's Instagram?
-Nope. Why?

14:53.434 --> 14:54.810
Yikes.

14:54.894 --> 14:55.728
What?

15:02.234 --> 15:05.529
Sir, is it true that Hwany's new title
will now be updated every Friday?

15:06.488 --> 15:07.323
Yes, it is.

15:07.406 --> 15:10.451
-You can't do that without telling me--
-Hey, you're not my boss!

15:10.534 --> 15:12.578
Hwany's a big name. You should've told me!

15:12.661 --> 15:15.497
It's been a while since Yun Song
had some healthy competition.

15:15.581 --> 15:18.083
This is a good thing. It's for the best.

15:20.711 --> 15:22.171
Was this, by chance,

15:23.714 --> 15:26.008
proposed by Producer Park?

15:29.428 --> 15:30.262
No.

15:35.726 --> 15:36.644
It really wasn't.

15:37.436 --> 15:39.063
It's not strong enough.

15:44.151 --> 15:46.570
The ending has to be more impactful.

15:47.071 --> 15:49.156
This is as impactful as it gets.

15:49.907 --> 15:52.117
I might really top the chart at this rate.

15:52.201 --> 15:53.786
You're daydreaming again.

15:54.411 --> 15:55.537
Okay.

15:55.621 --> 15:59.708
If I'm going to make it more impactful,
I'll have to speed up the early scenes.

16:00.209 --> 16:03.879
And the manager scene in the next episode,
why don't we move it up a little?

16:20.229 --> 16:21.981
Come on.

16:22.648 --> 16:24.942
I told you to pick up right away.

16:28.779 --> 16:33.158
You're the one who nudged me
And asked me out, aha

16:33.242 --> 16:36.745
I'm not the one who nudged you
And asked you out, aha

16:36.829 --> 16:37.830
SEO MI-RAE

16:37.913 --> 16:39.665
You lied to me all the time

16:39.748 --> 16:43.669
Saying you couldn't pick up my calls
Because your phone died

16:43.752 --> 16:45.629
I hate you so much, aha

16:45.713 --> 16:48.716
Say no more
And just hang up the phone

16:48.799 --> 16:50.884
Hang up!
I don't want to talk…

16:50.968 --> 16:53.929
Ms. Yun, why won't you answer your phone?

16:54.596 --> 16:57.433
My phone is crying, and so am I

16:57.516 --> 16:59.977
Holy crap! What the hell?

17:00.060 --> 17:02.229
-What are you doing?
-Come outside.

17:02.312 --> 17:04.648
You're hurting me! That hurts!

17:04.732 --> 17:05.566
Seriously!

17:06.900 --> 17:08.485
Are you out of your mind?

17:08.569 --> 17:11.321
Hey, how did you know where to find me?

17:11.405 --> 17:13.782
Your destinations are so predictable.

17:13.866 --> 17:16.452
Do you even know
what situation you're in right now?

17:16.535 --> 17:17.661
Yeah.

17:17.745 --> 17:19.163
Then what are you doing here?

17:20.039 --> 17:21.582
You're one to talk.

17:21.665 --> 17:24.251
You should've dealt with
the office politics for me.

17:24.334 --> 17:26.420
When they told you
he'd be moving to Friday,

17:26.503 --> 17:29.048
were you just standing there
with your arms wide open?

17:29.131 --> 17:30.215
That…

17:30.299 --> 17:33.218
It was so sudden.
I couldn't do anything about it.

17:33.302 --> 17:35.137
For the love of…

17:35.220 --> 17:37.556
First place? Fine, let him have it!

17:37.639 --> 17:38.932
What?

17:39.016 --> 17:41.560
Ms. Yun, you can't do that.

17:41.643 --> 17:44.605
Why not?
It's not like it would affect you much.

17:44.688 --> 17:47.524
Excuse me?
What do you mean, it wouldn't affect me?

17:47.608 --> 17:51.070
If your place drops the moment
I start working with you, what would Park…

17:51.570 --> 17:55.616
I mean, what would people out there
say about me?

17:56.241 --> 17:59.953
Plus, this kid had the nerve
to claw his way onto the same day as you

18:00.037 --> 18:01.663
to steal your spotlight.

18:01.747 --> 18:03.457
Shit.

18:03.540 --> 18:06.960
Are you really going to let him
get his way this easily?

18:07.044 --> 18:09.129
Damn it, seriously!

18:15.511 --> 18:17.054
This is driving me crazy.

18:18.680 --> 18:19.598
Thank you.

18:21.141 --> 18:23.519
Is it okay if I head out now--

18:24.353 --> 18:25.813
So freaking agonizing.

18:27.397 --> 18:29.858
So-yeong, you can go home now.

18:29.942 --> 18:30.776
Right.

18:34.780 --> 18:39.409
I feel like we'll come up with something
if we think just a little harder.

18:39.993 --> 18:42.788
-Got it.
-Oh, she's got it.

18:48.377 --> 18:49.503
Ms. Yun!

18:49.586 --> 18:53.549
We really need something new to happen
to Choi Si-woo right now.

18:53.632 --> 18:57.594
Define "new" for me. You said you weren't
a fan of his aunt kicking up a storm.

19:01.265 --> 19:03.267
My brain isn't working either.

19:06.228 --> 19:07.688
Should I kill off Choi Si-woo?

19:07.771 --> 19:11.441
If the main character dies,
everyone will come flocking, won't they?

19:12.651 --> 19:15.154
Please stop talking nonsense.

19:15.696 --> 19:16.864
Tell me.

19:17.489 --> 19:20.409
Why do you think TMTK became
my most successful work?

19:22.161 --> 19:23.662
Well, that's…

19:23.745 --> 19:27.416
That's because it allowed your talents
to truly shine.

19:28.125 --> 19:29.293
What are my talents?

19:30.419 --> 19:35.883
Well, you're really good
at drawing handsome men.

19:38.302 --> 19:39.761
Therein lies the problem.

19:40.512 --> 19:42.389
That was the problem from the start.

19:42.472 --> 19:44.975
It wasn't supposed to be a hit,

19:45.475 --> 19:48.145
but it came this far
because Choi Si-woo was too handsome.

19:48.729 --> 19:51.023
Choi Si-woo's looks are so immaculate

19:51.106 --> 19:55.194
that people can't stop reading
this incredibly boring slog!

19:55.277 --> 19:57.362
All because Choi Si-woo is too handsome!

19:57.946 --> 19:58.906
Seriously!

19:58.989 --> 20:02.743
I think I'm starting to understand
why Producer Cho left the company.

20:02.826 --> 20:03.827
Honestly,

20:04.995 --> 20:06.580
I want to end this series.

20:07.206 --> 20:09.208
I'm so sick and tired of it!

20:09.833 --> 20:10.667
Seo.

20:11.668 --> 20:13.754
Please save me.

20:15.672 --> 20:19.134
My whole life is falling apart.

20:25.140 --> 20:26.808
YOUR DAILY WARMTH, A PERFECT MOMENT

20:26.892 --> 20:29.436
Enjoying yourself?
We're dying here, you know.

20:29.519 --> 20:31.146
Do you think he really likes me?

20:31.230 --> 20:32.397
Hey, stop it.

20:32.481 --> 20:36.276
You've been talking about him all day.
Do you like him that much?

20:36.360 --> 20:38.987
It's just that he won't give me
a clear answer.

20:39.071 --> 20:41.698
Just go and ask him
if he actually likes you.

20:42.282 --> 20:43.992
Let's go ask him right now.

20:44.076 --> 20:44.910
Right now?

20:48.830 --> 20:52.167
Just go and ask him
if he actually likes you.

20:52.668 --> 20:54.920
Let's go ask him right now.

20:59.132 --> 21:02.052
Let's go ask him. Let's go. Just ask him.

21:02.135 --> 21:03.220
Let's ask. Should we?

21:03.303 --> 21:04.179
Let's go ask him.

21:04.263 --> 21:06.098
Just ask him. Should we go ask him?

21:06.181 --> 21:07.724
Let's ask him.

21:07.808 --> 21:09.351
Ask him.

21:24.741 --> 21:25.826
Come in.

21:27.452 --> 21:28.829
What? Where am I?

21:34.793 --> 21:37.963
What's this?
Why did you call me to your room?

21:40.340 --> 21:41.883
Too many eyes watching outside.

21:43.010 --> 21:43.927
I didn't see anyone.

21:47.180 --> 21:49.057
The moment I step out, they'll swarm.

21:51.393 --> 21:54.563
Hang in there.
Think about why you came here.

21:55.063 --> 21:56.023
What's with that look?

21:58.150 --> 21:59.401
But I must say,

22:00.819 --> 22:02.904
he's just so damn handsome.

22:06.199 --> 22:07.659
I have something to say--

22:07.743 --> 22:09.369
I believe you were a supervisor?

22:09.870 --> 22:11.788
-Don't come in starting tomorrow.
-What?

22:11.872 --> 22:13.123
Stop coming in to work.

22:15.500 --> 22:18.253
Wait, are you firing me right now?

22:18.337 --> 22:19.921
You could say that.

22:20.422 --> 22:22.049
I don't date company employees.

22:23.091 --> 22:24.676
If I'm to date you,

22:25.510 --> 22:26.762
I have to fire you.

22:30.140 --> 22:32.059
He's oblivious to labor laws.

22:32.934 --> 22:34.686
Why is he addressing me informally?

22:35.270 --> 22:36.271
Anything to say?

22:38.774 --> 22:42.903
I'm guessing every girl
you've ever asked out has said yes,

22:43.570 --> 22:45.155
but I'm not like that.

22:45.238 --> 22:47.407
-So?
-Show some effort.

22:47.491 --> 22:49.159
Show me what you're made of.

23:00.837 --> 23:02.964
You're more intriguing than I thought.

23:04.549 --> 23:07.761
It sounds like you want me to seduce you.
Is that right?

23:08.428 --> 23:11.348
Yes, seduce me.
Show me how it's done right now!

23:11.431 --> 23:13.350
I'm in a hurry. We don't have much time.

23:13.433 --> 23:15.102
On second thought, I won't fire you.

23:15.185 --> 23:18.146
No! You have to fire me.
Didn't you want to date me?

23:18.230 --> 23:22.025
I think I'll keep my eye on you
a bit longer.

23:22.943 --> 23:24.820
Don't do that! I told you I'm in a hurry.

23:25.570 --> 23:26.738
Yes, Mr. Choi.

23:27.781 --> 23:28.907
Choi.

23:33.912 --> 23:35.539
Reassign her to the secretary's office.

23:35.622 --> 23:36.623
Yes, sir.

23:36.706 --> 23:37.541
What is this now?

23:52.347 --> 23:54.015
-Aren't you leaving?
-What?

23:54.099 --> 23:55.851
I'm done talking. Leave now.

23:58.311 --> 23:59.479
What even…

24:32.637 --> 24:34.723
Allow me to introduce myself first.

24:34.806 --> 24:36.308
I'm the chief secretary,

24:36.391 --> 24:39.311
assisting the general manager
day and night, right by his side.

24:39.811 --> 24:43.148
My name is Choi Min-ju.

24:43.231 --> 24:45.025
CHIEF SECRETARY
CHOI MIN-JU

24:45.108 --> 24:46.943
As I'm sure you know,

24:47.527 --> 24:51.406
the secretary's office at SY Group
is a demanding department.

24:52.324 --> 24:54.701
Though you may have parachuted in,
Mr. Choi insists

24:54.784 --> 24:58.705
we follow at least the basic protocol,
so he specifically asked me

24:59.206 --> 25:01.875
to carry out a simple job interview.

25:02.375 --> 25:04.294
An interview? My interview?

25:04.377 --> 25:07.380
Yes. I simply need your honest answers.

25:07.464 --> 25:08.965
What is your favorite food?

25:09.049 --> 25:09.883
Food?

25:11.760 --> 25:15.514
I… Well, I like beef and pork.

25:15.597 --> 25:16.556
BEEF, PORK

25:17.140 --> 25:19.976
And… I just like all kinds of meat.

25:20.060 --> 25:21.019
What about hobbies?

25:21.102 --> 25:23.563
What kind of date would you like to go on?

25:23.647 --> 25:25.732
Where would you like to travel?

25:29.069 --> 25:31.696
-Is this really an interview?
-What is your ideal type?

25:32.864 --> 25:36.034
He should be asking me himself.
Why is he having others do it?

25:36.117 --> 25:37.744
Excuse me.

25:40.497 --> 25:41.957
Yes, Mr. Choi?

25:42.040 --> 25:43.083
Yes.

25:43.166 --> 25:44.167
I see.

25:44.668 --> 25:46.836
Allergies and shoe size.

25:47.337 --> 25:48.964
Yes, I'll check right away.

25:49.464 --> 25:51.383
Yes, I'll be right there.

25:52.467 --> 25:54.970
Mr. Ko! Why haven't we left yet?

25:55.554 --> 25:57.180
There's a car blocking us.

25:58.807 --> 26:01.101
Mr. Choi insists that we hurry along.

26:01.184 --> 26:03.019
Not going anywhere, are you?

26:04.813 --> 26:06.731
Hey! My apologies.

26:06.815 --> 26:08.441
This really brings me back.

26:08.942 --> 26:11.194
Hey! You punk!

26:13.405 --> 26:15.282
I'm going to take care of it.

26:17.742 --> 26:18.618
Hey!

26:19.578 --> 26:22.581
Wait, is that really necessary?

26:22.664 --> 26:23.957
-It's okay.
-Hey!

26:24.040 --> 26:25.750
Mr. Ko isn't your average person.

26:31.506 --> 26:32.716
Taken care of.

26:38.471 --> 26:41.600
Did they really need to include this part
from the webtoon?

26:45.770 --> 26:48.523
Ms. Seo, Mr. Choi would like to see you.

26:50.317 --> 26:51.318
This way, please.

26:56.323 --> 26:57.866
Mr. Choi

26:58.575 --> 27:00.660
does not like it when people knock twice.

27:01.286 --> 27:03.455
Going forward, when you're knocking,

27:03.538 --> 27:06.958
a single gentle tap will suffice.

27:09.419 --> 27:11.254
-This is ridiculous.
-Excuse me?

27:12.922 --> 27:13.798
Nothing.

27:14.299 --> 27:16.885
Why don't you give it a try? A gentle tap.

27:16.968 --> 27:18.094
A gentle tap.

27:24.225 --> 27:25.310
Come in.

27:25.852 --> 27:26.686
You may enter.

27:26.770 --> 27:29.939
By the way, that was a little too loud.

27:32.942 --> 27:36.112
That annoying woman.
She's just like in the webtoon.

27:56.675 --> 27:57.884
What is all this?

27:59.511 --> 28:00.345
Flowers.

28:01.429 --> 28:03.306
The best way to win a woman over.

28:06.351 --> 28:08.770
Hey! You shouldn't have.

28:11.648 --> 28:12.732
Look.

28:13.441 --> 28:18.196
I may be seducing you, but I expect
a bit more respect from you than "hey."

28:26.037 --> 28:27.455
So? Do you like it?

28:29.874 --> 28:30.709
Kinda.

28:32.377 --> 28:33.294
You're picky.

28:39.384 --> 28:41.344
So, what's next?

28:42.178 --> 28:43.805
There's got to be a next step.

28:43.888 --> 28:45.640
You have it all prepared, don't you?

28:50.478 --> 28:52.522
How could someone be so shameless?

28:54.858 --> 28:56.192
You didn't prepare a date?

28:57.277 --> 28:59.028
Come with me.

29:06.745 --> 29:07.579
This is weak.

29:08.663 --> 29:09.664
What?

29:10.165 --> 29:13.084
I said this is weak.
This will never satisfy our read…

29:13.168 --> 29:16.004
I mean, do you think this will satisfy me?

29:16.588 --> 29:17.922
What are you talking about?

29:18.423 --> 29:19.674
It hasn't even started yet.

29:42.572 --> 29:44.699
I figured you should eat
before we go on a date.

29:45.366 --> 29:46.242
Try it.

29:53.416 --> 29:55.919
It actually tastes like food!

29:57.128 --> 29:57.962
No way.

30:12.602 --> 30:15.605
How did I end up owing my life
to a woman like that?

30:22.320 --> 30:24.113
A sudden trip to the department store?

30:25.532 --> 30:26.366
Are you…

30:27.826 --> 30:31.746
Given my social standing, I can't take you
on a date without stopping by here first.

30:32.705 --> 30:33.832
Oh my God!

30:44.300 --> 30:45.134
Go on.

30:45.635 --> 30:46.886
Try them on.

30:57.772 --> 30:58.606
Whoa.

30:58.690 --> 30:59.816
Would you like to try it on?

30:59.899 --> 31:00.733
YES

31:22.171 --> 31:23.214
Do you like it?

31:37.645 --> 31:41.190
Why would you rent the entire pool
if you're not going to swim?

31:41.274 --> 31:43.067
Why? Do you not approve?

31:43.985 --> 31:45.111
It's not bad.

31:52.327 --> 31:53.328
Seo Mi-rae.

32:03.129 --> 32:05.048
What do you think? Do you like it?

32:08.551 --> 32:09.719
Not sure.

32:10.345 --> 32:12.180
I think I might like it.

32:39.290 --> 32:40.541
You're late.

32:52.720 --> 32:53.888
I get it now.

32:55.181 --> 32:56.015
This

32:56.975 --> 32:58.393
isn't a cliché, but…

33:01.104 --> 33:03.398
Ms. Yun! Open up!

33:04.983 --> 33:06.275
You know what time it is?

33:06.359 --> 33:08.236
Ms. Yun, I got it.

33:08.319 --> 33:09.404
-I got it!
-Got what?

33:10.697 --> 33:12.699
I realized what Choi Si-woo needs to do.

33:12.782 --> 33:13.700
What?

33:14.325 --> 33:16.244
Let's go back to the beginning.

33:16.327 --> 33:17.161
The beginning?

33:17.245 --> 33:21.249
You said this webtoon could become a hit
because of Si-woo's handsome looks.

33:21.332 --> 33:22.166
I did.

33:22.250 --> 33:25.795
Plus, the fantasy of him being a chaebol
who can give you everything you want.

33:25.878 --> 33:29.340
But you said people are hating on it
because the chaebol thing was so cliché.

33:29.424 --> 33:31.009
No, I was wrong.

33:31.592 --> 33:32.802
-You were wrong?
-Listen.

33:32.885 --> 33:36.556
Choi Si-woo is not a cliché.
He's a classic.

33:37.140 --> 33:39.976
The definition of classic
that female readers desire.

33:40.059 --> 33:42.395
Women were raving about TMTK

33:42.478 --> 33:44.856
for offering an escape
from their harsh reality,

33:44.939 --> 33:49.694
but all those cheesy lines you gave Si-woo
ended up giving them the ick.

33:50.278 --> 33:51.237
So what's your point?

33:51.863 --> 33:53.406
We've totally got this.

33:53.990 --> 33:57.994
Let's get back to the drawing board
and give them a true chaebol romance.

34:01.080 --> 34:03.624
First, the department store.
Let's start there.

34:03.708 --> 34:04.917
-Yeah?
-The luxury floor.

34:05.001 --> 34:05.835
The luxury floor?

34:08.171 --> 34:12.300
Seeing Si-woo suddenly lose his composure
really made my heart flutter…

34:12.800 --> 34:14.218
I mean, I'm saying it would.

34:14.302 --> 34:16.220
-So, pull up his top?
-So-yeong.

34:16.304 --> 34:18.806
We could use some darker coloring here.

34:18.890 --> 34:20.933
-And the ring.
-The ring?

34:21.017 --> 34:23.144
-The ring is too small.
-It needs to be bigger?

34:23.227 --> 34:25.229
At least this big.

34:25.313 --> 34:26.689
You heard her. Leave it to me.

34:26.773 --> 34:29.442
Si-woo comes over, grabs her wrist,
and drags her away.

34:29.525 --> 34:31.152
She will feel a vibe.

34:31.235 --> 34:33.321
Game over. Classic.

34:40.912 --> 34:42.622
EUN NA-RA, SHINE FOR ME, BY MY SIDE

35:07.688 --> 35:09.941
-Here to buy coffee?
-Yes.

35:10.024 --> 35:11.692
Iced latte, please.

35:11.776 --> 35:14.362
One iced latte. That will be 5,000 won.

35:26.541 --> 35:28.960
We'll be working late together
before every deadline.

35:30.753 --> 35:31.587
I guess.

35:37.218 --> 35:38.427
You know I didn't mean to.

35:39.512 --> 35:42.390
You make it sound
like it was a car accident.

35:43.474 --> 35:45.059
You seem mad at me. That's why.

35:46.227 --> 35:47.186
I'm not.

35:47.270 --> 35:48.396
Doors opening.

35:56.904 --> 35:59.866
Is that your habit? Putting on a front?

36:01.826 --> 36:03.661
Doors closing.

36:04.328 --> 36:07.748
It shows, anyway.
You're terrible at keeping a poker face.

36:10.293 --> 36:11.544
-Is that right?
-Yes.

36:12.128 --> 36:14.755
Then why ask me, you jerk?

36:18.801 --> 36:21.137
I guess you'll also be here for a while.

36:21.971 --> 36:23.472
-Me?
-Yes.

36:23.556 --> 36:25.057
I noticed you had two cups of coffee.

36:26.893 --> 36:30.396
I got another one while the café was open
so I can have it on my way home.

36:30.479 --> 36:32.231
It tastes bad when the ice melts.

36:32.315 --> 36:35.318
I know. I plan on clocking out
before the ice melts.

36:36.861 --> 36:38.446
Doors opening.

36:40.573 --> 36:41.574
Me too.

37:04.055 --> 37:05.264
1 MESSAGE

37:05.348 --> 37:06.682
Damn it.

37:17.735 --> 37:18.653
Shit.

37:19.779 --> 37:21.697
Are you kidding me?

37:24.825 --> 37:27.203
No. I shouldn't nag her.

37:29.038 --> 37:30.373
Don't you nag her.

37:37.880 --> 37:39.090
Come on!

37:43.552 --> 37:44.553
YUN SONG
&lt;TMTK&gt; E110

37:48.683 --> 37:49.600
It's over.

38:01.362 --> 38:03.072
By now…

38:12.540 --> 38:13.874
3: PlanC
HWANY

38:14.667 --> 38:16.168
1: THE MAN TO KNOW
YUN SONG

38:19.755 --> 38:21.924
First place!

38:22.425 --> 38:24.051
First place!

38:24.135 --> 38:27.471
First place, first place
First place is mine

38:27.555 --> 38:31.183
First place
It doesn't change hands easily

38:40.526 --> 38:41.861
Congratulations, Mi-rae!

38:41.944 --> 38:43.154
Congratulations!

38:43.237 --> 38:44.238
-Congrats!
-Hello.

38:44.322 --> 38:45.197
Hi.

38:46.574 --> 38:47.408
Congratulations!

38:47.491 --> 38:48.868
Congratulations!

38:57.543 --> 38:59.045
Seo Mi-rae!

39:00.004 --> 39:00.921
Hi.

39:01.005 --> 39:01.881
Morning!

39:03.466 --> 39:04.300
Oh dear.

39:05.134 --> 39:06.719
Who turned you around?

39:19.482 --> 39:20.316
Well defended.

39:23.569 --> 39:25.196
Did something happen?

39:26.989 --> 39:29.241
Hey, did something happen here?

39:36.165 --> 39:37.416
Let's get to work, okay?

39:43.214 --> 39:44.632
Nailed it, Yun Song!

39:44.715 --> 39:46.258
She's finally back on track.

39:46.342 --> 39:48.052
She poured her soul into this one.

39:48.135 --> 39:49.637
A triumphant return for TMTK!

39:50.137 --> 39:52.681
"Hella fun"? I wouldn't go that far.

40:08.072 --> 40:09.490
Good times.

40:55.995 --> 40:58.706
It's only a dinner.
Did you have to bring a private jet?

40:58.789 --> 40:59.957
Don't approve of this either?

41:02.084 --> 41:03.669
What took you so long?

41:05.546 --> 41:08.299
I have to stick to my hours.
I'm just an employee, after all.

41:09.216 --> 41:11.844
You make your boss wait,
then use work as an excuse?

41:14.054 --> 41:15.723
Where are we having dinner tonight?

41:15.806 --> 41:17.224
You'll see. Come with me.

41:31.864 --> 41:32.740
Look!

41:34.950 --> 41:35.951
Dolphins!

42:02.811 --> 42:05.147
Let's get engaged. I'll handle my parents.

42:07.775 --> 42:08.776
Engaged?

42:09.818 --> 42:10.653
Are you mad?

42:12.238 --> 42:14.615
You answered a chaebol's proposal
with a spit take?

42:16.325 --> 42:19.370
Didn't I tell you?
We're just dating, nothing more.

42:19.453 --> 42:20.538
What?

42:22.540 --> 42:24.250
I told you not to fall for me.

42:58.117 --> 42:59.285
It's so pretty.

43:05.457 --> 43:06.584
Mi-rae.

43:07.167 --> 43:08.002
Yeah?

43:08.711 --> 43:09.670
Let's do it your way.

43:10.588 --> 43:11.422
My way?

43:12.506 --> 43:14.508
We don't have to get engaged.

43:18.512 --> 43:19.680
In exchange…

43:21.932 --> 43:24.602
can you at least be my girlfriend?

43:31.150 --> 43:33.319
I've never asked anyone
for anything before.

43:55.215 --> 43:56.258
Do I have to

43:57.760 --> 43:59.178
ask for this too?

44:02.890 --> 44:04.350
Is he…

44:04.933 --> 44:05.768
What…

44:25.079 --> 44:27.790
Dopamine overload!

44:45.474 --> 44:46.767
Why look away?

44:48.435 --> 44:49.353
Did I?

44:52.981 --> 44:54.024
I got something.

45:07.663 --> 45:10.999
I'm giving this to you as a boyfriend,
so don't turn it down.

45:11.500 --> 45:12.501
That's all it means.

45:14.086 --> 45:15.170
Si-woo!

45:49.663 --> 45:51.498
Oh my God!

46:07.055 --> 46:07.890
What?

46:07.973 --> 46:09.016
What's going on?

46:16.607 --> 46:17.733
What's happening?

46:18.776 --> 46:19.610
Hello!

46:21.487 --> 46:25.491
Ms. Seo Mi-rae, your 50 hours
of dating Choi Si-woo have ended.

46:25.574 --> 46:26.617
What did you say?

46:26.700 --> 46:27.993
SERVICE PERIOD EXPIRED

46:28.076 --> 46:29.077
No!

46:30.120 --> 46:31.288
Si-woo!

46:31.914 --> 46:33.081
Damn it!

46:40.214 --> 46:41.215
What was that?

46:51.642 --> 46:54.561
"You can only date a male character
for up to 50 hours"?

46:57.981 --> 46:58.899
No.

47:00.567 --> 47:01.568
No.

47:01.652 --> 47:04.029
No!

47:04.905 --> 47:06.865
We have a meeting with Mipare tomorrow.

47:06.949 --> 47:11.328
Okay. Both of them are on the rise,
so we must sign their upcoming titles.

47:11.411 --> 47:12.621
-Yes, sir!
-And Team 1?

47:12.704 --> 47:14.873
I contacted Hwan-su,

47:15.624 --> 47:18.919
but they want to finish the series first,
so that's on hold for now.

47:19.002 --> 47:21.255
Choi Si-woo left a lasting impression.

47:24.967 --> 47:26.260
What?

47:28.846 --> 47:30.013
God!

47:30.097 --> 47:32.599
So much so
that he threw my life off balance.

47:34.643 --> 47:36.770
Looks that surpass
his webtoon counterpart,

47:36.854 --> 47:39.606
great conversation skills,
and subtle thoughtfulness.

47:39.690 --> 47:41.817
It was definitely too much…

47:53.120 --> 47:55.330
and yet, his sexiness made it all okay.

47:56.623 --> 47:57.958
Hella sexy.

47:58.041 --> 48:04.047
HELLA SEXY

48:04.715 --> 48:06.758
DEVICE SATISFACTION
USER EXPERIENCE REVIEW

48:08.051 --> 48:11.722
As expected from a producer,
it's a very well-written review.

48:12.264 --> 48:13.098
That's a relief.

48:13.181 --> 48:16.894
It's fascinating that you got matched
with a character from one of your works.

48:16.977 --> 48:19.104
So how was it?
Tell me what you really think.

48:20.689 --> 48:22.441
What exactly do you mean?

48:23.233 --> 48:26.486
I just want to hear your honest opinion.

48:29.406 --> 48:32.409
It was fun. Well, more than fun.

48:33.744 --> 48:35.621
Then why did you end it so soon?

48:36.914 --> 48:40.250
I think I've experienced enough
to understand what it's about,

48:40.334 --> 48:43.921
and Choi Si-woo set the bar
way too high from the get-go, so…

48:46.173 --> 48:47.132
Ms. Seo.

48:47.925 --> 48:48.759
Yes?

48:48.842 --> 48:51.470
There are still 899 characters left.

48:51.553 --> 48:53.764
What makes you so sure
Si-woo is the best one?

48:57.142 --> 49:01.647
If you throw away your remaining hours,
you might regret it later on.

49:08.195 --> 49:13.533
I think she knows she probably shouldn't,
but she can't help being drawn in.

49:14.368 --> 49:15.535
Who is he?

49:16.036 --> 49:18.789
-It's like I'm watching a movie.
-He drives women crazy.

49:18.872 --> 49:20.874
-Totally.
-Yeah, those eyes…

49:20.958 --> 49:22.876
He just melts your heart.

49:22.960 --> 49:25.045
-He draws you in.
-The way he holds her hand!

49:25.128 --> 49:26.338
Dopamine.

49:27.756 --> 49:29.800
I need my dopamine!

49:41.269 --> 49:43.814
There are still 899 characters left.

49:43.897 --> 49:46.066
What makes you so sure
Si-woo is the best one?

49:46.817 --> 49:50.946
If you throw away your remaining hours,
you might regret it later on.

49:53.365 --> 49:54.199
He's right.

49:54.282 --> 49:59.121
It's a one-month subscription trial,
so why don't I make full use of that?

50:00.455 --> 50:02.541
Since when did I ever turn down freebies?

50:03.250 --> 50:04.835
Stop kidding yourself.

51:13.028 --> 51:15.864
Looks like you've lucked out
on another amazing pick today.

51:17.365 --> 51:18.200
Hurry along now.

51:18.909 --> 51:23.497
I did let Min Jun-young talk me into
returning, but I was still skeptical.

51:24.331 --> 51:27.459
Could there really be a man more thrilling

51:27.959 --> 51:31.254
and charming than Choi Si-woo,
a webtoon male lead?

51:31.338 --> 51:33.173
What's wrong? Is there a problem?

51:34.132 --> 51:35.550
Give me a second.

51:36.343 --> 51:38.762
My, you're a handful.

51:40.680 --> 51:41.515
Now…

51:47.687 --> 51:49.189
Hey, don't push…

52:51.835 --> 52:53.670
But once again,

52:54.754 --> 52:58.133
Boyfriend on Demand managed
to far exceed my expectations.

55:57.354 --> 56:02.359
Subtitle translation by: Daham Yoon
